<main style="max-width: 1120px; margin: auto; padding: 1rem; display: grid; gap: 1rem; padding-bottom: 2rem;">
  <h1 style="font-size: 1.875rem; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 2rem;">Privacy Policy</h1>
  
  <p style="font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.5;">
    At TryAgain, we highly prioritize the privacy and security of our users. This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, and safeguard the information you provide when using our comprehensive party application, SupremeParty.
  </p>

  <h2 style="font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 1.5rem;">1. About SupremeParty</h2>
  <p style="font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.5;">
    SupremeParty is a comprehensive party and social gaming application that includes multiple mini-games and interactive experiences such as:
    <ul style="margin-top: 0.5rem;">
      <li><b>Piramide:</b> A drinking game with interactive elements and potential in-app purchases.</li>
      <li><b>LoHi Party:</b> A social guessing game for entertainment.</li>
      <li><b>Culture Party:</b> A cultural knowledge and trivia-based party game.</li>
      <li><b>Additional Games:</b> Various other party games and interactive experiences that may be added over time.</li>
    </ul>
    Due to the nature of these games, content may vary in appropriateness and some games may involve alcohol-related themes.
  </p>

  <h2 style="font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 1.5rem;">2. Information We Collect</h2>
  <p style="font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.5;">
    We collect the following information to provide and improve our comprehensive gaming service:
    <ul style="margin-top: 0.5rem;">
      <li><b>Account Information:</b> If you choose to create an account, we may collect username, email address, and basic profile information.</li>
      <li><b>Usage Data:</b> Information about how you use the app, including game selections, interactions, session duration, and engagement metrics across all games.</li>
      <li><b>Game Data:</b> Scores, progress, preferences, and gameplay statistics for each game within the SupremeParty ecosystem.</li>
      <li><b>Room Data:</b> Information related to multiplayer game rooms you create or join, stored temporarily in Firebase Realtime Database.</li>
      <li><b>Player Responses:</b> Content provided during gameplay including answers, questions, and interactive responses shared with other players.</li>
      <li><b>Custom Content:</b> User-generated questions, scenarios, or content created within various games.</li>
      <li><b>Purchase Data:</b> Information related to in-app purchases, subscriptions, and premium features, handled securely by RevenueCat.</li>
      <li><b>Device Information:</b> Device type, operating system, app version, and technical specifications to optimize performance across all platforms.</li>
      <li><b>Location Data:</b> General location information (if permitted) to provide region-appropriate content and comply with local regulations.</li>
      <li><b>Social Interactions:</b> Friend connections, party invitations, and social features within the app ecosystem.</li>
    </ul>
  </p>

  <h2 style="font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 1.5rem;">3. How We Use Your Information</h2>
  <p style="font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.5;">
    The information we collect is used to:
    <ul style="margin-top: 0.5rem;">
      <li>Provide and maintain all games and features within the SupremeParty application.</li>
      <li>Facilitate multiplayer gaming experiences and real-time interactions between players.</li>
      <li>Process and manage in-app purchases, subscriptions, and premium content access.</li>
      <li>Personalize your gaming experience based on preferences and gameplay history.</li>
      <li>Provide customer support and respond to user inquiries across all games.</li>
      <li>Improve and optimize individual games and the overall app experience.</li>
      <li>Ensure fair play and prevent cheating or abuse of game mechanics.</li>
      <li>Analyze usage patterns to enhance game balance and introduce new features.</li>
      <li>Send important updates, notifications, and promotional content (with your consent).</li>
      <li>Comply with legal obligations and ensure age-appropriate content delivery.</li>
      <li>Maintain app security and protect against fraud and unauthorized access.</li>
    </ul>
  </p>

  <h2 style="font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 1.5rem;">4. Game-Specific Data Handling</h2>
  <p style="font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.5;">
    Different games within SupremeParty may handle data differently:
    <ul style="margin-top: 0.5rem;">
      <li><b>Piramide:</b> Tracks drinking game progress, purchase history for premium features, and gameplay preferences.</li>
      <li><b>LoHi Party:</b> Stores guessing game statistics, player performance, and social interaction data.</li>
      <li><b>Culture Party:</b> Maintains trivia performance, cultural knowledge progress, and educational content preferences.</li>
      <li><b>Social Games:</b> Manages party room data, player responses, voting systems, and temporary social connections.</li>
      <li><b>Custom Games:</b> Handles user-generated content, custom scenarios, and personalized game modes.</li>
    </ul>
    All game data is processed with the same security standards and privacy protections outlined in this policy.
  </p>

  <h2 style="font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 1.5rem;">5. User-Generated Content</h2>
  <p style="font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.5;">
    SupremeParty allows extensive user-generated content across multiple games:
    <ul style="margin-top: 0.5rem;">
      <li>Content provided by users is their responsibility and should comply with our community guidelines.</li>
      <li>User-generated content may vary significantly in maturity level depending on the game and participants.</li>
      <li>We do not actively monitor or moderate all user-generated content but reserve the right to remove inappropriate material.</li>
      <li>Content is shared only with participants in the same game room or session.</li>
      <li>Users retain ownership of their content but grant us license to use it within the app ecosystem.</li>
      <li>We expressly disclaim responsibility for the accuracy, appropriateness, or legality of user-generated content.</li>
      <li>Content creation features may be restricted based on age verification and regional compliance.</li>
    </ul>
  </p>

  <h2 style="font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 1.5rem;">6. Age Restrictions and Content Maturity</h2>
  <p style="font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.5;">
    Given the diverse nature of games within SupremeParty:
    <ul style="margin-top: 0.5rem;">
      <li><b>Piramide:</b> Requires users to be of legal drinking age in their jurisdiction (18+ or 21+ depending on location).</li>
      <li><b>General Party Games:</b> Recommended for users aged 17+ due to potential mature content and social interactions.</li>
      <li><b>Trivia Games:</b> Generally suitable for users 13+ but may contain mature themes.</li>
      <li>Age verification may be required for certain games or features.</li>
      <li>Parents and guardians are responsible for supervising minors' use of the application.</li>
      <li>Content filtering options are available but not guaranteed to catch all inappropriate material.</li>
    </ul>
  </p>

  <h2 style="font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 1.5rem;">7. Data Security and Storage</h2>
  <p style="font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.5;">
    We implement comprehensive security measures to protect your information:
    <ul style="margin-top: 0.5rem;">
      <li>All data is encrypted in transit and at rest using industry-standard protocols.</li>
      <li>Firebase security rules restrict data access to authorized users and sessions only.</li>
      <li>Game room data and temporary social interactions are automatically deleted after sessions end.</li>
      <li>Payment information is processed securely through RevenueCat and never stored on our servers.</li>
      <li>Regular security audits and updates are performed to maintain data protection standards.</li>
      <li>Employee access to user data is strictly limited and monitored.</li>
      <li>Data backups are encrypted and stored in secure, geographically distributed locations.</li>
    </ul>
  </p>

  <h2 style="font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 1.5rem;">8. Third-Party Services and Integrations</h2>
  <p style="font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.5;">
    SupremeParty integrates with various third-party services to enhance functionality:
    <ul style="margin-top: 0.5rem;">
      <li><b>Firebase:</b> Real-time database, authentication, analytics, and cloud functions for multiplayer experiences.</li>
      <li><b>RevenueCat:</b> Subscription and purchase management for premium features and content.</li>
      <li><b>Analytics Platforms:</b> App usage analysis, crash reporting, and performance monitoring.</li>
      <li><b>Social Media Integration:</b> Optional sharing features and social login capabilities.</li>
      <li><b>Content Delivery Networks:</b> Fast and reliable delivery of game assets and media content.</li>
      <li><b>Push Notification Services:</b> Game invitations, updates, and important communications.</li>
      <li><b>Audio/Video Processing:</b> Enhanced multimedia experiences within certain games.</li>
    </ul>
    These services may collect information according to their own privacy policies, which we encourage you to review.
  </p>

  <h2 style="font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 1.5rem;">9. Data Sharing and Disclosure</h2>
  <p style="font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.5;">
    We do not sell your personal information. We may share data in the following circumstances:
    <ul style="margin-top: 0.5rem;">
      <li><b>With Other Players:</b> Game-related information necessary for multiplayer experiences.</li>
      <li><b>Service Providers:</b> Third-party services that help us operate and improve the app.</li>
      <li><b>Legal Requirements:</b> When required by law, court order, or government regulation.</li>
      <li><b>Business Transfers:</b> In the event of a merger, acquisition, or sale of business assets.</li>
      <li><b>Safety and Security:</b> To protect users' safety and prevent fraud or abuse.</li>
      <li><b>Aggregated Data:</b> Anonymized, aggregated statistics for research and improvement purposes.</li>
    </ul>
  </p>

  <h2 style="font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 1.5rem;">10. International Data Transfers</h2>
  <p style="font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.5;">
    SupremeParty is available globally, and your data may be transferred to and processed in countries other than your own:
    <ul style="margin-top: 0.5rem;">
      <li>We ensure appropriate safeguards are in place for international data transfers.</li>
      <li>Data processing complies with applicable international privacy frameworks.</li>
      <li>Regional data residency requirements are respected where legally mandated.</li>
      <li>Cross-border transfers are limited to what is necessary for service provision.</li>
    </ul>
  </p>

  <h2 style="font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 1.5rem;">11. Your Data Protection Rights</h2>
  <p style="font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.5;">
    Depending on your location, you may have the following rights regarding your personal data:
    <ul style="margin-top: 0.5rem;">
      <li><b>Access:</b> Request copies of your personal data and information about how it's processed.</li>
      <li><b>Rectification:</b> Request correction of inaccurate or incomplete personal information.</li>
      <li><b>Erasure:</b> Request deletion of your personal data under certain conditions.</li>
      <li><b>Restriction:</b> Request limitation of processing your personal data in specific circumstances.</li>
      <li><b>Objection:</b> Object to processing of your personal data for direct marketing or legitimate interests.</li>
      <li><b>Data Portability:</b> Request transfer of your data to another service provider in a structured format.</li>
      <li><b>Withdrawal of Consent:</b> Withdraw previously given consent for data processing.</li>
      <li><b>Automated Decision-Making:</b> Request human review of automated decisions that significantly affect you.</li>
    </ul>
    To exercise these rights, please contact us at <a href="mailto:hello@tryagain.app" style="color: blue; text-decoration: none;">hello@tryagain.app</a> with your request and verification information.
  </p>

  <h2 style="font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 1.5rem;">12. Children's Privacy</h2>
  <p style="font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.5;">
    SupremeParty contains games with varying age appropriateness:
    <ul style="margin-top: 0.5rem;">
      <li>We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13 without parental consent.</li>
      <li>Certain games require age verification and are restricted to adults.</li>
      <li>Parents can request access to, modification of, or deletion of their child's information.</li>
      <li>Parental controls and content filtering options are available for younger users.</li>
      <li>Educational games may be designed for younger audiences with appropriate privacy protections.</li>
    </ul>
  </p>

  <h2 style="font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 1.5rem;">13. Data Retention</h2>
  <p style="font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.5;">
    We retain different types of data for varying periods:
    <ul style="margin-top: 0.5rem;">
      <li><b>Account Data:</b> Retained while your account is active and for a reasonable period after deletion.</li>
      <li><b>Game Session Data:</b> Temporary data deleted immediately after game sessions end.</li>
      <li><b>Purchase Records:</b> Retained for tax and legal compliance purposes as required by law.</li>
      <li><b>Analytics Data:</b> Aggregated and anonymized data may be retained indefinitely for improvement purposes.</li>
      <li><b>Support Communications:</b> Retained for customer service purposes and legal compliance.</li>
    </ul>
  </p>

  <h2 style="font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 1.5rem;">14. Marketing and Communications</h2>
  <p style="font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.5;">
    We may use your information for marketing purposes:
    <ul style="margin-top: 0.5rem;">
      <li>Promotional emails about new games, features, and special offers (with your consent).</li>
      <li>Push notifications about app updates, game invitations, and important announcements.</li>
      <li>Personalized recommendations for games and features based on your preferences.</li>
      <li>You can opt out of marketing communications at any time through app settings or email unsubscribe links.</li>
    </ul>
  </p>

  <h2 style="font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 1.5rem;">15. Changes to This Privacy Policy</h2>
  <p style="font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.5;">
    We may update this Privacy Policy to reflect changes in our practices or legal requirements:
    <ul style="margin-top: 0.5rem;">
      <li>Material changes will be communicated through the app or email notification.</li>
      <li>Continued use of the app after changes constitutes acceptance of the updated policy.</li>
      <li>Version history and effective dates are maintained for transparency.</li>
      <li>We encourage periodic review of this policy to stay informed about data practices.</li>
    </ul>
  </p>

