  <p style="font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.5;">
    For questions, concerns, or requests regarding this privacy policy or your personal data:
    <ul style="margin-top: 0.5rem;">
      <li><b>General Inquiries:</b> <a href="mailto:hello@tryagain.app" style="color: blue; text-decoration: none;">hello@tryagain.app</a></li>
      <li><b>Privacy Concerns:</b> <a href="mailto:privacy@tryagain.app" style="color: blue; text-decoration: none;">privacy@tryagain.app</a></li>
      <li><b>Data Protection Requests:</b> <a href="mailto:dpo@tryagain.app" style="color: blue; text-decoration: none;">dpo@tryagain.app</a></li>
    </ul>
